1417
01:42:35,960 --> 01:42:38,200
subsequent to the setting
of condition 1Sq...

1418
01:42:38,280 --> 01:42:41,600
for strategic missile launch...

1419
01:42:41,680 --> 01:42:44,720
on board the USS Alabama
on 1 November.

1420
01:42:44,800 --> 01:42:49,200
Now, based on the testimony
from personnel on board the Alabama...

1421
01:42:49,240 --> 01:42:53,920
and, in no small measure, to that
of the senior officer, Captain Ramsey...

1422
01:42:54,000 --> 01:42:56,480
I am prepared to make
my recommendations to SUBPAC.

1423
01:42:56,560 --> 01:43:01,040
- Without my testimony, sir?
- You have a problem with that?

1424
01:43:01,120 --> 01:43:06,160
- I might, sir.
- I have known Captain Ramsey
for almost 30 years.

1425
01:43:06,240 --> 01:43:08,640
We served together
on more than a few occasions.

1426
01:43:08,720 --> 01:43:12,200
If he is lying, this will be
the first I've heard of it.

1427
01:43:12,280 --> 01:43:16,080
- Yes, sir.
- My primary concern here...

1428
01:43:16,160 --> 01:43:18,520
is the breakdown in the system.

1429
01:43:18,600 --> 01:43:21,400
In this instance,
the system failed...

1430
01:43:21,440 --> 01:43:26,200
because the two senior officers did not
work to resolve their differences...

1431
01:43:26,240 --> 01:43:28,760
while preserving
the chain of command.

1432
01:43:28,840 --> 01:43:32,200
Now you may have been
proven right, Mr. Hunter...

1433
01:43:32,280 --> 01:43:35,400
but insofar as
the letter of the law is concerned...

1434
01:43:35,480 --> 01:43:37,720
you were both right.

1435
01:43:37,800 --> 01:43:40,920
And you were also both wrong.

1436
01:43:41,000 --> 01:43:45,640
This is the dilemma that will
occupy this panel, this Navy...

1437
01:43:45,720 --> 01:43:49,240
and this country's armed forces
as a whole...

1438
01:43:49,320 --> 01:43:51,600
long after you leave this room.

1439
01:43:53,760 --> 01:43:59,000
Off the record, you've both
created one hell of a mess:

1440
01:43:59,040 --> 01:44:03,080
A mutiny aboard a United States
nuclear submarine...

1441
01:44:03,160 --> 01:44:07,800
violation of nuclear
launch protocol.

1442
01:44:10,960 --> 01:44:13,520
For the record, it is
the conclusion of this panel...

1443
01:44:13,600 --> 01:44:16,440
that your actions
aboard the Alabama...

1444
01:44:16,480 --> 01:44:19,280
were consistent with
the best traditions of the Navy...

1445
01:44:19,320 --> 01:44:21,240
and in the interests
of the United States.

1446
01:44:21,280 --> 01:44:26,000
As such, the recommendations
of this panel will be to accept...

1447
01:44:26,040 --> 01:44:29,680
in a manner reflective of his long
and dedicated service to his country...

1448
01:44:29,760 --> 01:44:35,160
Captain Ramsey's request
for early retirement from active duty.

1449
01:44:35,240 --> 01:44:40,680
And based, in no small part,
on Captain Ramsey's recommendation...

1450
01:44:40,760 --> 01:44:44,280
that Lieutenant Commander Hunter
be given his next command...

1451
01:44:44,360 --> 01:44:48,000
at the earliest possible convenience.

1452
01:44:48,080 --> 01:44:52,320
Unless, of course, you wish
to challenge these recommendations.

1453
01:44:52,400 --> 01:44:54,240
No, sir.

1454
01:44:54,320 --> 01:44:57,120
- Captain Ramsey?
- No, sir.

1455
